Dashboard 5
CAI Email Campaign summary is our main dashboard consists of 7 sheets 
There is an Action Created on this dashboard on the heat map to go to the other dashboard 
This Action takes you to another dashboard with more detail on CAI Group name. For example, if you select in Class group name

1.Total Emails sent by CAI Group

  • Data is filtered on Email and all Ali email
  • The color shows open Rate
  • Size shows the sum of email opens
  • The marks are labeled by CAI  group name, the sum of total  Email sent, the sum of Email opens and Open Rate


2.Open Rate

Sum of Total email sent vs Open rate, on this scatter plot Color shows details about CAI Group Name, Size shows the sum of Total Email sent The data is Filtered on Email

A calculated field is used to calculate open Rate 

    



3. Severity Email %

  • The color shows details about C severity Name
  • The Size shows the sum of Total email sent
  • Marks are labeled by % of total email sent
  • The data is filtered on CAI Group name and Email
